== 爭議 ==
=== 歧視亞洲消費者並使用籠飼雞蛋 ===
好市多因在亞洲購物中心裡販售籠飼雞蛋而備受批評，它是台灣唯一尚未公開承諾停止使用籠飼雞蛋的大型超市，其競爭對手[[大潤發|大潤發]]是台灣市場率先考慮販售放養雞蛋的零售商<ref>Auchan Retail’s Cage-Free Eggs Policy </ref>。 2019年11月，大型超市巨頭[[家樂福|家樂福]]（Carrefour）承諾在台灣落實100％放養計劃<ref>{{Cite web|title=Carrefour Taiwan first supermarket in Asia to pledge cage-free egg policy|url=https://www.eyeontaiwan.com/carrefour-taiwan-first-supermarket-in-asia-to-pledge-cage-free-egg-policy|accessdate=2019-12-13|date=2018-05-21|work=Eye On Taiwan|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212140236/https://www.eyeontaiwan.com/carrefour-taiwan-first-supermarket-in-asia-to-pledge-cage-free-egg-policy|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

好市多讓美國和歐洲的消費者能夠選擇購買[[放養雞蛋|放養雞蛋]]，並聲稱致力於「五種動物的自由」，其中包括「免於不適並隨時都能自然表現本能」 <ref>{{Cite web|title=Animal Welfare|url=https://www.costco.com/sustainability-animal-welfare.html|accessdate=|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210216163653/https://www.costco.com/sustainability-animal-welfare.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 但是，許多研究得出的結論是，籠中飼養的母雞本能不能表現，例如張開翅膀或沐浴灰塵<ref>{{Cite web|title=Key reasons why laying hens suffer in farming|url=https://www.rspca.org.uk/adviceandwelfare/farm/layinghens/keyissues|accessdate=2019-12-13|work=www.rspca.org.uk|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212134733/https://www.rspca.org.uk/adviceandwelfare/farm/layinghens/keyissues|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由於好市多無法公開承諾在台灣和亞洲商店販售放養雞蛋，引起許多人指責好市多[[歧視|歧視]]亞洲消費者且支持虐待動物<ref>{{Cite web|title=Costco: Filth, Cruelty and Discrimination {{!}}|url=http://costco-eggs.com/|accessdate=2019-12-13|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212134734/http://costco-eggs.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

好市多在2020年12月宣布，他們將在全球範圍內禁止籠養雞蛋。<ref>{{cite news |title=Costco transitioning to cage-free eggs worldwide |url=https://www.meatpoultry.com/articles/24191-costco-transitioning-to-cage-free-eggs-worldwide |work=報紙 |publisher=Meat + Poultry |accessdate=2020-12-31 |archive-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124150340/https://www.meatpoultry.com/articles/24191-costco-transitioning-to-cage-free-eggs-worldwide |dead-url=no }}</ref>好市多亦將成為第一家美國零售商發布在全球供應鏈中限制籠養動物的政策。<ref>{{cite news |title=Costco is making this major change to its egg products |url=https://www.yahoo.com/amphtml/lifestyle/costco-making-major-change-egg-120913885.html |agency=Yahoo Life |accessdate=2020-12-31 |archive-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124150309/https://www.yahoo.com/amphtml/lifestyle/costco-making-major-change-egg-120913885.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>好市多的財務規劃和投資者關係總監Josh Dahmen亦表示「我們正在朝著非籠養雞蛋的方向進行過渡。 隨著時間的流逝，我們將繼續提高百分比，目標是最終達到百分百。」<ref>{{cite news |title=Costco to ban the use of cages in its global supply chain |url=https://www.poultryworld.net/Eggs/Articles/2020/12/Costco-to-ban-the-use-of-cages-in-its-global-supply-chain-682905E/ |accessdate=2020-12-31 |work=報紙 |agency=Poultry World |archive-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124150334/https://www.poultryworld.net/Eggs/Articles/2020/12/Costco-to-ban-the-use-of-cages-in-its-global-supply-chain-682905E/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

